    <lb n="10"/>γενέ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">σθαι</supplied>.  καὶ σαυτοῦ δ᾽ <app type="BL"><lem resp="8.489"><expan>ἐπ<ex cert="high">ιμέλου</ex></expan></lem><rdg><expan>ἐπ<ex cert="high">ιμελόμενο?</ex></expan></rdg></app> ἵν᾽ <expan>ὑ<ex cert="high">γιαίνηις</ex></expan>, 
